headline: TempraMed Announces Strategic Agreement with Maccabi Healthcare Services, a Leading HMO with over 2.8 Million Patients
summary: Vancouver, British Columbia--(Newsfile Corp. - December 8, 2025) - TempraMed Technologies Ltd. (CSE: VIVI) ("TempraMed" or the "Company"), a medical technology innovator transforming how temperature-sensitive medications are stored and managed, is pleased to announce a major commercial milestone as part of its broader global expansion strategy: its flagship products, the VIVI Cap and VIVI EPI, are now available through Maccabi Healthcare Services, Israel's second-largest health maintenance...
